## 4. mt CLI クイックリファレンス

詳細は `~/.agi-tools/mini-tachyon/docs/CLI.md`。エージェントが頻繁に使うものを抜粋:

```bash
# BL 操作
mt bl create --title <T> --project <P> --category <C> [--id <ID>] [--priority high|normal|low|urgent]
mt bl update <id> --state in_progress|completed|...|blocked
mt bl add-decision <id> --type answer|commitment|scope_change|deferred --by user|ai --content "..."
mt bl add-question <id> --content "..." [--from-task <task_id>]
mt bl list [--state X] [--project Y] [--ids id1,id2] [--today-selected] [--human]
mt bl get <id> [--human]

# Deliverable
mt deliverable update-state <id> --state unreviewed|reviewing|done|needs_revision|generating [--comment "..."]
mt deliverable add-comment <id> --content "..." [--by user|ai]
mt deliverable get <id> [--human]

# Cockpit
mt cockpit spawn --instruction <I> [--directory <D>] [--agent-type claude|codex|...] [--bl <id>]
mt cockpit send <task_id> --text "..." [--fallback-instruction <I>]

# Daily Loop
mt morning start
mt morning finalize <deliverable_id> --selections '[{"bl":"BL-XXXX","action":"approve","spawn_class":"A"}]'
mt evening start

# クエリ
mt today selected [--human]
mt projects list [--human]
```

### 出力規約
- デフォルト: stdout に JSON
- `--human`: 人間向け整形
- エラー: stderr に `{error, message, detail?}` の JSON、exit 1
- エラーは zod validate / not_found / conflict / cockpit / io 等の構造化された code を返す

